{"tid":2179349,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《黑豹》男主角查特域克保斯曼患癌去世　終年43歲","createTime":"2020-08-29T04:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T04:59:57.000Z","uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3df9ed48645baeea5a0fd64919c86eb69b84be47","tid":2179349,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:51:02.000Z","msg":"電影《黑豹》男主角、飾演鐵查拉的影星查特域克保斯曼因為癌病去世，終年43歲。<br />\n<br />\n家人稱，查特域克保斯曼在洛杉磯家中去世，妻子和家人陪伴在側。<br />\n<br />\n查特域克保斯曼生前未有公開談及患癌的事。<br />\n<br />\n家人的聲明說，查特域克保斯曼2016年被診斷患上第3期結腸癌，並在過去4年，在癌病進入第4期時與之博鬥，形容他是真正的鬥士，帶來很多大家喜愛的電影，又說他能夠在《黑豹》中演繹國王鐵查拉的角色，是演員生涯的榮幸。 <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546648-20200829.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546648-20200829.htm&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZrVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=6269479c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546648-20200829.htm&h=d81ddf0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546648-20200829.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0bc05b1196893f198109edd6fda4d65039ab437b","tid":2179349,"uid":191510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n死得咁突然"}]}